		and conditions in their entirety. If you do not agree with any of these terms,
		please do not use this site.
	</p>

	<h2>2. Description of Services</h2>
	<p>
		VanDev offers custom software development services, including but not limited to:
		web development, desktop applications, SaaS platforms, industrial artificial
		intelligence solutions, and technology consulting.
	</p>
	<p>
		The information presented on this site is for informational purposes and does not
		constitute a contractual offer. Specific terms for each project are agreed upon
		individually with each client.
	</p>

